{"tid":1540763,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要破林鄭功，必需再搞大型和理非遊行","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:08:33.000Z","uid":276734,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7e68c4181268ad317d3b4009365d763ca0b8190d","tid":1540763,"uid":276734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:28:15.000Z","msg":"今次林鄭撤例明顯試圖打擊國際輿論,令香港人嘅五大訴求被忽略，甚至連Ted Cruz 都比佢迷惑到。但係要破林鄭功其實唔難,　就係9月8號之後以「五大訴求，缺一不可」搞一個浩大嘅和理非遊行。<br />\n<br />\n當200萬香港人再度上街個陣，所有外媒都會問「點解香港人仲上街？唔係撤例啦咩?」我地就可以借佢地把口宣傳「五大訴求，缺一不可」呢個宣傳將會非常有力。<br />\n<br />\n而政府一定唔應充訴求，當外媒一報道政府唔應充訴求，外國制裁同勇武就可以全面進埸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要再搞200萬人大遊行，而且必需和理非。咁先可以破林鄭功。"},{"pid":"951c09ae0d7e387bebf5b31c52e7aa49a5d47e2a","tid":1540763,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:28:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"444d5f72afc54d40cb5b352aeacacf41081d829f","tid":1540763,"uid":128388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:28:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第六訴求</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7Yt9JA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7Yt9JA.jpg&h=c1d70329&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4okoYBW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4okoYBW.jpg&h=be2da638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b811f495d67df39cb2ba1eb6ff8c0b3aed776c4","tid":1540763,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:29:43.000Z","msg":"［文宣外交］Reddit幫到我哋對付林鄭假撤回！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540697\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540697</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"afd8cac4a2f9f27964bfae85c8d26701dbf1c63d","tid":1540763,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:31:28.000Z","msg":"10萬人都唔知有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b446052d3a4